headline: Q3 Earnings Highlights: Gartner (NYSE:IT) Vs The Rest Of The IT Services & Consulting Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how it services & consulting stocks fared in Q3, starting with Gartner (NYSE:IT).
